313-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/star-wars-outlaws-impact-star-wars-1313-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/star-wars-outlaws-impact-star-wars-1313-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/star-wars-outlaws-impact-star-wars-1313-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/star-wars-outlaws">《星球大战：神枪手》</a></em>是第一款开放世界的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars">星球大战</a></em>游戏，自发布以来就一直被拿来与<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/brands/naughty-dog">顽皮狗</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/uncharted">《神秘海域》</a>进行比较，而导演对此感到非常高兴。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/star-wars-outlaws-could-be-the-dream-star-wars-game-youre-looking-for-3764864">“星球大战亡命之徒”可能是您正在寻找的梦想“星球大战”游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《星球大战：亡命之徒》</em>将于 8 月 30 日上映，故事背景设定在<em>《帝国反击战》</em>和<em>《绝地归来》</em>之间。玩家将跟随恶棍兼走私犯凯·维斯 (Kay Vess) 穿越人迹罕至的外缘，与银河系最臭名昭著的犯罪家族合作。</p><p> <em>《星球大战：亡命之徒》</em>于去年夏天首次公布，并将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/star-wars-outlaws-will-feature-red-dead-redemption-style-wanted-system-3455904">采用通缉系统</a>，类似于<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto">《侠盗猎车手》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/red-dead-redemption-2"><em>《荒野大镖客：救赎》</em></a>中的通缉系统。该游戏的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/star-wars-outlaws-is-inspired-by-movie-making-tricks-of-the-1970s-3470973">灵感也很大程度上来自 20 世纪 70 年代电影制作的实用性</a>。然而，粉丝们不断地将<em>《亡命之徒》</em>与<em>《神秘海域》</em>进行比较，这是一款关于环球旅行宝藏猎人的动作冒险游戏。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">进一步确认这可能是我十多年来一直想要的《星球大战：神秘海域》游戏<a href="https://t.co/0D4tVUarZp">https://t.co/0D4tVUarZp</a></p><p> — Brian Bumpiss（彼得·奥斯汀）（@ThatPeterAustin） <a href="https://twitter.com/ThatPeterAustin/status/1777756476536222070?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 4 月 9 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “这不一定是我们的参考点，”创意总监 Julian Gerighty 告诉<em><a href="https://www.videogameschronicle.com/features/interviews/star-wars-outlaws-interview-uncharted-is-a-wonderful-game-to-be-compared-to/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VGC</a></em> 。 “这是一款非常棒的游戏，如果你要与某人进行比较，它可能是业内最好的，”他补充道。 “顽皮狗和他们所做的事情绝对是出色的。我会接受它，[但]这不是起源点。”</p><p> “ <em>《星球大战亡命之徒》</em>中有太多我们想要讲述的故事和要遇到的角色，”他补充道。 “时间表是完美的，那里有很大的潜力。”</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/star-wars-outlaws-could-be-the-dream-star-wars-game-youre-looking-for-3764864">试玩预览</a>后<em>，《NME》</em>写道：“在捕捉遥远星系这个真实存在的角落中的浮渣和罪恶时，《星球大战亡命之徒》将其爪子伸进去——如果开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ubisoft">育碧</a>能够抚平战斗中的粗糙边缘，这可能最终成为有史以来最好的星球大战游戏之一。”</p><p>在其他消息中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">《Elden Ring》</a></em>玩家在最近推出的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-expansion-dlc-3766304">《Shadow Of The Erdtree》</a></em>扩展包中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-players-having-issues-with-shadow-of-the-erdtree-dlc-3768089">遇到了麻烦</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/star-wars-outlaws-director-pleased-with-uncharted-comparisons-3768112">《星球大战：法外之徒》导演对《神秘海域》的比较很满意，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Red Velvet 携受《仲夏夜惊魂》启发的《Cosmic》音乐录影带回归https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-velvet-cosmic-music-video-release-3768081?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=red-velvet-cosmic-music-video-releaseGladys Yeo Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:04:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3768081 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Red Velvet 2024新音乐回归喜悦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们的第七张同名迷你专辑现已发行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-velvet-cosmic-music-video-release-3768081">Red Velvet 回归后，带着受《仲夏夜惊魂》启发的《Cosmic》音乐录影带</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Red Velvet 2024新音乐回归喜悦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/red-velvet-joy-new-music-comeback-2024-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">韩国流行</a>女团<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-velvet">Red Velvet</a>发行了新迷你专辑《Cosmic》，该专辑也纪念了女团成立十周年。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/red-velvet-im-not-sure-if-we-can-say-that-weve-helped-define-k-pop-3559500">Red Velvet：“我不确定我们是否可以说我们帮助定义了韩国流行音乐”</a></strong></li></ul><p> Red Velvet 今天（6 月 24 日）发布了《Cosmic》，并发布了同名主打单曲的音乐视频。该剪辑的灵感来自 2019 年恐怖电影<em>《仲夏夜惊魂》</em> （如音乐视频片尾卡所示），并讲述了女团加入乡村社区时的冒险经历。</p><p> <em>“爱是宇宙/我骑着你的节奏/穿越太阳系/跟我来/你和我，穿越黑夜/宇宙之爱”，</em>四重奏在这首受迪斯科影响的时髦舞曲中演唱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Red Velvet 레드벨벳 &#39;Cosmic&#39; MV" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FyG21rXCxlY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>除了主打歌外，新唱片还收录了《Sunflower》、《Last Drop》、《Love Arcade》、《Bubble》和《Night Drive》等五首新歌。成员姜涩琪在 SM Entertainment 上传的<a href="https://m.post.naver.com/viewer/postView.naver?volumeNo=38030548&amp;memberNo=41350603" target="_blank" rel="noopener">采访</a>中表示：“多亏了 [&#39;Cosmic&#39;s] 的旋律和和声，就像宇宙一样广阔，你将能够感受到夏夜的凉爽，而不是炎热的夏日。” 。</p><p>在《Cosmic》发行之前，该女团还宣布即将进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-velvet-2024-happiness-my-dear-reve1uv-asia-tour-3766782">2024 年“幸福：亲爱的，ReVe1uv”亚洲巡演</a>。 Red Velvet 今年八月将在首尔举办两晚演出，随后还将在曼谷、雅加达、马尼拉和澳门演出。</p><p>在其他韩国流行音乐新闻中，流行的韩国夏季音乐节 Waterbomb 宣布了今年晚些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/waterbomb-los-angeles-2024-everything-you-need-to-know-3768029">在洛杉矶举办为期两天的活动</a>的日期。定于今年九月在 Dignity Health Sports Park 举行，这将是该节日首次登陆洛杉矶。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-velvet-cosmic-music-video-release-3768081">Red Velvet 回归后，带着受《仲夏夜惊魂》启发的《Cosmic》音乐录影带</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
